761
00:40:03,802 --> 00:40:04,802
"Nanti."

762
00:40:05,137 --> 00:40:07,347
"Jadi awak jangan berani
pergi tempat lain."

763
00:40:08,974 --> 00:40:10,475
Ya, saya hafal nota awak.

764
00:40:11,643 --> 00:40:13,978
Tulisan tangan awak sangat bagus.

765
00:40:13,979 --> 00:40:15,188
Ia kelihatan seperti seorang gadis.

766
00:40:15,439 --> 00:40:17,231
Kerana rakan sekelas saya,

767
00:40:17,232 --> 00:40:19,233
