- Dia berkata bercakap dengannya.

811
00:41:55,122 --> 00:41:56,122
Hah?

812
00:41:59,793 --> 00:42:01,545
Kitty, awak sangat comel.

813
00:42:03,839 --> 00:42:06,841
Awak, awak dengar
perbualan orang lain.

814
00:42:06,842 --> 00:42:08,176
